    public class ScheduledCall
extends AbstractChatsDomainEntity
implements java.lang.Comparable<ScheduledCall>, org.incode.module.note.dom.api.notable.Notable
    ScheduledCall indicates a call to a Participant by a Volunteer to be made in the future. ScheduledCalls will have status of 'completed' once the call has beebn made by the Volunteer. ScheduledCalls are generally managed by a CalendarDayCallSchedule
